author: SILVIA TURCHI
title: SILVIA TURCHI
text:
I rented a car twice with them in Bcn.
The vehicles I rented the first time had some problem
RAAc service been super nice
And helpful
With zero cost
Or extra charge from Autoclick.
Customer service super professional
And very friendly.
I recommend them.
:-)
Good job guys!
